Flag link
  Description: Build the link plugin
  Default: false

Library link_plugin
  Build$: flag(everything) || flag(link)
  XMETADescription: links external functions in the BIR program with an existing library in the Knowledge base
  Path: plugins/link
  FindlibName: bap-plugin-link
  CompiledObject: best
  BuildDepends: bap, bap-core-theory, bap-knowledge, core_kernel, graphlib, regular
  InternalModules: Link_main
  XMETAExtralines: tags="pass,analysis,link"
